267
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:22,190
- Here. 
- I shouldn't receive this reward without deserving it.

268
00:20:22,190 --> 00:20:24,390
However, this is a gift from my elder after all.

269
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:25,800
If I don't accept it,

270
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:29,280
