271
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:31,850
As long as you like it.

272
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:35,520
There are barely any womenfolk in this family.

273
00:20:35,520 --> 00:20:39,590
I'm absolutely delighted that you could marry into this family.

274
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:42,790
I hope that when you have time in the future, you'll come and chat with me.

275
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:45,690
Most definitely! I'm someone who loves chatting.

276
00:20:45,690 --> 00:20:49,260
Since the Third Young Master has been unwell each day,

277
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:51,400
I'm afraid you'd be overly worried

278
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:54,930
so I also prepared a big surprise for you.

279
00:20:54,930 --> 00:20:56,300
Just wait and see.

280
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:58,820
I'm someone who loves surprises!

281
00:20:58,820 --> 00:21:00,790
Thank you so much, Second Madam.

282
00:21:00,790 --> 00:21:03,120
You'll like it for sure!

283
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:05,970
Then, I won't disturb you any longer.

284
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:07,990
Have a good rest.

285
00:21:07,990 --> 00:21:10,640
Good bye, Second Madam.

286
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:12,630
Come by often.

287
00:21:12,630 --> 00:21:14,390
Okay.

288
00:21:14,390 --> 00:21:16,750
- Bye bye, princess. 
- Bye bye.

289
00:21:22,170 --> 00:21:23,900
What was she here for?

290
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:27,510
Shiqing, I think that

291
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:32,060
Second Madam is pretty nice. She even brought you tonics.

292
00:21:32,060 --> 00:21:33,210
Throw it away.

293
00:21:33,210 --> 00:21:36,170
They're so expensive, don't throw them away!

294
00:21:36,170 --> 00:21:37,850
Okay, I will. I'll throw them away.

295
00:21:37,850 --> 00:21:40,890
I just think that even though something's up with the Second Madam,

296
00:21:40,890 --> 00:21:43,420
the tonics are fine. It'd be a shameful waste.

297
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:45,550
There's nothing else?

298
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:48,400
- Nope. 
- Really?

299
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:50,580
Why would I lie to you?

300
00:21:50,580 --> 00:21:53,200
Also, I'm the princess!

301
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:56,880
Can I be easily attributed for this small favor?

302
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,960
How funny.

303
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,290
I hope it is so.

304
00:22:02,530 --> 00:22:05,920
Siheng, take me for a walk.

305
00:22:18,620 --> 00:22:21,170
Madam, if you don't like Third Young Master Mei,

306
00:22:21,170 --> 00:22:23,640
then why did you have to bring him tonics?

307
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:25,130
You must not know.

308
00:22:25,130 --> 00:22:28,350
These things have been sitting around for so long.

309
00:22:28,350 --> 00:22:31,760
It just sits there, giving it to them,

310
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:34,660
it is only to ask for a favor of the Princess.

311
00:22:34,660 --> 00:22:37,060
Madam, you are wise.

312
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:39,120
There are tons of these things.

313
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:42,710
Remember that when you're bringing things over later on,

314
00:22:42,710 --> 00:22:46,320
Be smart and intelligent, get some news.

315
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:47,810
Yes.

316
00:22:48,280 --> 00:22:49,600
Wait.

317
00:22:50,900 --> 00:22:54,080
What I told you to do - how is it coming along?

318
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:56,650
Don't worry, Madam. What you have told us to do

319
00:22:56,650 --> 00:22:59,120
all the servants are doing their best to accomplish.

320
00:23:00,820 --> 00:23:02,900
The Princess has just entered the manor,

321
00:23:02,900 --> 00:23:06,820
so it naturally takes some effort to bring her to our side.

322
00:23:10,280 --> 00:23:14,640
You are more close with Second Madam, do you know what she gave us to look at?

323
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:17,100
I only know that in order to make you happy,

324
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:19,100
she spent some effort.

325
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:23,240
Is it that you're jealous I have better relations with people here?

326
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:30,560
My Lord, look, they're here.

327
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:34,280
- Princess.
- Second Madam, what do you want to show us?

328
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:37,590
Today, I spent a lot of money to invite the best acrobatics group

329
00:23:37,590 --> 00:23:40,000
to relieve everyone's boredom.

330
00:23:40,810 --> 00:23:43,190
Come on, let's go onto the balcony.

331
00:23:43,190 --> 00:23:44,340
- Let them begin.
- Yes.

332
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:47,240
- My Lord, let's go.
- Let's go.

333
00:23:50,850 --> 00:23:52,310
Have a seat.

334
00:23:53,260 --> 00:23:55,920
My Lord, the acrobatic group that I invited today

335
00:23:55,920 --> 00:23:59,970
has a special skill that's really famous.

336
00:23:59,970 --> 00:24:02,470
She spent a lot of money to invite an acrobatics group?

337
00:24:02,470 --> 00:24:05,280
My father and I are the best.

338
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:07,120
Speaking of father,

339
00:24:07,120 --> 00:24:10,050
I don't know where he is right now.

340
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:14,930
I'm Wang Haiquan, the master of the Qiankun troop and I

341
00:24:14,930 --> 00:24:17,020
give my greetings to General and Madam.

342
00:24:17,020 --> 00:24:19,560
I give my greetings to Young Master and Princess.

343
00:24:19,560 --> 00:24:21,650
Our troop has traveled the world for a long time.

344
00:24:21,650 --> 00:24:24,980
We will definitely give a good show for everyone to watch.

345
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:27,960
The Princess is here today, do your best!

346
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:30,950
Since the Princess esteems us, we'll do our best.

347
00:24:30,950 --> 00:24:32,990
[Good show and time]

348
00:24:32,990 --> 00:24:35,550
- Great! 
- Amazing!

349
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:43,390
- Impressive! Great! 
- Amazing!

350
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:07,950
Next up is our main event,

351
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:11,150
Boulder-Shattering Chest. From our audience,

352
00:25:11,150 --> 00:25:13,630
who would like to come forth and try?

353
00:25:13,630 --> 00:25:15,400
Me!

354
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:18,130
- Can you even? 
- Yes.

355
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:21,150
Second Young Master,

356
00:25:22,570 --> 00:25:25,250
take the hammer.

357
00:25:28,290 --> 00:25:30,080
It's pretty heavy.

358
00:25:37,290 --> 00:25:38,940
My goodness.

359
00:25:41,430 --> 00:25:44,470
Young Master, perhaps you didn't sleep well last night.

360
00:25:44,470 --> 00:25:46,140
Here, let me.

361
00:25:46,140 --> 00:25:49,000
Let me! Let me, let me! Let me.

362
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:51,350
Let me do it.

363
00:25:53,890 --> 00:25:55,590
I'm here.

364
00:25:55,590 --> 00:25:57,380
Princess, you mustn't!

365
00:25:57,380 --> 00:26:00,110
Don't worry, move aside.

366
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:03,420
Princess, your body is fragile and precious, maybe you shouldn't...

367
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:06,220
Don't worry, trust me!

368
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:21,890
The Princess is indeed an honorable woman.

369
00:26:25,020 --> 00:26:28,510
Oh no, I've blown my cover.

370
00:26:29,250 --> 00:26:32,810
If it weren't for all of my hits earlier, there's no way she could have broken it!

371
00:26:32,810 --> 00:26:34,620
Right! Exactly.

372
00:26:34,620 --> 00:26:37,830
I, well, I took advantage of your work.

373
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:39,650
Thanks, Second Young Master.

374
00:26:45,030 --> 00:26:47,870
Princess, let me have the hammer.

375
00:26:56,280 --> 00:27:01,050
Lu Yingyao, doesn't behave like a Princess.

376
00:27:01,050 --> 00:27:04,440
Almost like someone from Jianghu. 

377
00:27:14,210 --> 00:27:16,150
I didn't scare you just then, did I?

378
00:27:16,150 --> 00:27:17,740
No.

379
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:22,050
Here.

380
00:27:22,050 --> 00:27:23,720
You cannot see anything.

381
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:26,640
Why do you come to the study all day long?

382
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:30,340
Since I cannot see, why don't you explain it to me?

383
00:27:37,210 --> 00:27:38,920
What is it?

384
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:44,200
I catched a cold, my throat doesn't feel well.

385
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:47,980
Since that's the case, then I won't bother you.

386
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:50,540
What lucky day is it today?

387
00:27:50,540 --> 00:27:53,230
It's better if I go back to the room and stay there.

388
00:27:55,150 --> 00:28:00,540
Shiqing, you have a good rest. I will return to my room.

389
00:28:04,130 --> 00:28:05,770
Hold on.

390
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:11,160
Shiqing, what is it?

391
00:28:12,850 --> 00:28:15,830
After a few days, it is my Teacher's birthday.

392
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:18,250
I want you to help me write a letter.

393
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:25,030
Write a letter? That's such a secret matter.

394
00:28:25,030 --> 00:28:28,630
It is better not to let me write it for you.

395
00:28:28,630 --> 00:28:32,720
I don't mind. We are husband and wife.

396
00:28:38,650 --> 00:28:42,080
Who's close with you?

397
00:28:42,080 --> 00:28:47,500
Could it be... that you do not know how to write?

398
00:28:47,500 --> 00:28:50,550
What a joke!

399
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:52,940
How could a princess possibly not know how to write?!

400
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:55,790
Of course I can write.

401
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:59,940
I will just write it. You will not be able to see it anyway.

402
00:29:00,830 --> 00:29:02,440
Come on.

403
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:11,290
Tell me. What do you want me to write?

404
00:29:12,330 --> 00:29:15,410
I will speak, you go write.

405
00:29:16,670 --> 00:29:20,520
Dear teacher, please accept my respects.

406
00:29:21,490 --> 00:29:23,730
It has been many days since we parted.

407
00:29:23,730 --> 00:29:27,120
I don't know if your health is well.

408
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:28,920
The weather in the capital changes a lot.

409
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:32,020
I hope you take good care of your health.

410
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:38,270
Please continue. You do not have to wait for me. I write fast.

411
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:43,320
My body is not well, I cannot go attend the birthday feast.

412
00:29:43,320 --> 00:29:45,320
I am really remorseful.

413
00:29:47,130 --> 00:29:49,820
Good thing my Father taught me a few words before.

414
00:29:49,820 --> 00:29:52,320
Looks like it really is put to use.

415
00:29:58,730 --> 00:30:01,240
Boulder-Shattering Chest

416
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:10,860
Bad news! Qiao Yun, bad news!

417
00:30:10,860 --> 00:30:13,720
-What's the matter?
-Third Young Master Mei just asked me to write a letter!

418
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:15,330
Do you know how to write?

419
00:30:15,330 --> 00:30:20,440
I don't know. I just know how to write "Boulder-Shattering Chest".

420
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:24,220
What did Third Young Master Mei say to you?

421
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:26,160
- He said "Thank you, Teacher".
- "Thank you, Teacher."

422
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:29,300
- Asked him to take care of himself and that he can't attend the birthday.
- Take care of himself.

423
00:30:29,300 --> 00:30:30,780
- Can't attend the birthday.
- Can't attend the birthday...

424
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:33,150
Princess!

425
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:37,410
Xiao Ran, what are you doing here?

426
00:30:37,410 --> 00:30:40,360
I am here to bring something from Second Madam. Madam has advised

427
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:43,380
