428
00:30:43,380 --> 00:30:45,480
Just put it here.

429
00:30:46,190 --> 00:30:50,480
You guys are making soup? I am good at making soups! Do you need help?

430
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:53,350
Are looking down on me? Xiao Ran?

431
00:30:53,350 --> 00:30:55,630
Please do not misunderstand, older sister.

432
00:30:55,630 --> 00:30:57,990
Then I will not bother you.

433
00:30:57,990 --> 00:30:59,760
I'm leaving.

434
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:04,690
Quickly help me write the letter to replace the one I wrote.

435
00:31:04,690 --> 00:31:06,730
It will be bad if he sends it.

436
00:31:06,730 --> 00:31:09,410
Okay. Then help me look after the soup. I will be back at once.

437
00:31:09,410 --> 00:31:11,310
Okay, okay.

438
00:31:32,740 --> 00:31:37,130
These tonics are top-quality. He's got it good.

439
00:31:37,780 --> 00:31:39,870
I'll help him replenish some.

440
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,980
So fast!

441
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:49,540
That's pretty much what he wants to say.

442
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,850
If you send it now,

443
00:31:52,850 --> 00:31:55,890
then the meaning should be about the same.

444
00:32:00,450 --> 00:32:01,860
Quickly go. Quickly.

445
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:04,390
Run faster. Don't expose yourself.

446
00:32:22,090 --> 00:32:26,910
Shiqing, this soup I have made myself. Try it.

447
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:53,620
Third Young Master Mei...

